com.cloudera.labs.envelope.spark

Class RowWithSchema

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cloudera.labs.envelope.spark.RowWithSchema
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Row

    public class RowWithSchema
extends Object
implements Row
    Allows individual Spark SQL Rows to be created with a schema. This is achieved by simply wrapping a RowFactory-created Row and overriding the schema methods.
